data.description:
Discover just off 599 in Aldea, this warm and inviting single level home with a large coyote fenced yard and recently updated with tile flooring, new appliances, wall finishes to name just a few.  Well separated bedrooms and versatile room use is possible.  Set on a quiet street with a large two car garage and with extra parking and easy care landscaping.

Aldea de Santa Fe includes over 200 acres of parks with tennis, bocce, pickle, and basketball courts plus walking trails to enjoy during the day and dark skies at night to see all the heavens you missed in town.
